        "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
        "body": "Checks have also been added to the colour handler registration events.\r\n\r\nI think those are the only other events that would cause problems here, unless anyone else can think of something?\r\n\r\nThe section concerned is in `Minecraft.init()`, between the calls to `beginMinecraftLoading` and `finishMinecraftLoading`. It's important to try to do as little as possible in the event of an error here, mainly to avoid a 'cascade' of errors making troubleshooting difficult.",
