        "author_association": "MEMBER",
        "body": "I think the issue is that we are collecting mod errors so we can display a bunch, instead of just crashing right away.\r\nFor some stuff like version mismatches and missing mods, it makes sense to collect up and display those all at once. Trying to continue running at all after an unknown crash from a mod doesn't really make sense to me.",
