    {
        "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
        "body": "This is for those kind of things though?\r\n\r\nAs far as I'm aware, loading only continues here to display an error screen in those cases where it's useful.\r\n\r\nIn order to actually get to display that screen, though, we need to not crash in the meantime. If some initialisation is skipped, but later initialisation isn't, that becomes much harder to achieve reliably.\r\n",
